  <title>Installing other browsers</title>

  <p>Unfortunately, Endless does not currently support the installation of other
  browsers.</p>

  <p>We plan on supporting the installation of other browsers at a future date,
  and will notify you when we add this feature. Feel free to give us your
  feedback and let us know what you need.</p>

  <p>In the meantime, we hope you enjoy using the current Endless browser to
  explore new websites and stay updated on the world's news!</p>
